---

---

<section class="mx-4 my-16 lg:mx-auto container">
    <div class="relative bg-indigo-950 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-16 shadow-2xl group">

        <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-80 h-80 bg-purple-600/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] transition-all group-hover:bg-purple-600/30"></div>
        <div class="absolute -left-20 -bottom-20 w-80 h-80 bg-cyan-600/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] transition-all group-hover:bg-cyan-600/30"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-col items-start justify-between gap-10">

            <div class="text-center lg:text-left space-y-4 max-w-2xl">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tight">
                   Tu Destino Mexico se actualiza
                </h2>
                <p class="text-indigo-200 text-lg md:text-xl font-medium opacity-90">
                    Tus reservaciones, cupones y tus XoloCoins a la palma de la mano descargala.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-5">
                <a
                        href="#"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
                        aria-label="Descargar en App Store"
                >
                    <img
                            src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3c/Download_on_the_App_Store_Badge.svg"
                            alt="Disponible en App Store"
                            class="h-14 md:h-13 w-auto"
                    />
                </a>

                <a
                        href="#"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
                        aria-label="Descargar en Google Play"
                >
                    <img
                            src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/78/Google_Play_Store_badge_EN.svg"
                            alt="Disponible en Google Play"
                            class="h-14 md:h-13 w-auto"
                    />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>